<paragraph id="E07536B6FE96FEF05889F8FCFE35668F" blockId="347.[151,1437,1687,2038]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FE96FEF05914F8FDFDB366F3" author="Rondani, C." box="[266,512,1904,1931]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" pagination="193 - 231" refId="ref369428" refString="Rondani, C. (1865 c) Diptera italica non vel minus cognita descripta vel annotata observationibus nonnullis additis. Fasc. II. Muscidae. Atti della Societa Italiana di Scienze Naturali, 8, 193 - 231." type="journal article" year="1865">Rondani (1865c: 202)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FE96FEF05A67F8FDFCFC66F3" box="[633,847,1904,1930]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Platychyra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FE96FEF05A67F8FDFCFC66F3" box="[633,847,1904,1930]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">Platychyra robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from just the male sex, without specifying either the 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FE96FEF058D9F819FEAE66D7" box="[199,285,1940,1966]" family="Number" pageId="347" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
or the length of the specimens. We found 
<specimenCount id="F6CCFD3FFE96FEF05AF1F818FCC666D6" box="[751,885,1941,1967]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" type="generic" typeStatus="syntype">one syntype</specimenCount>
in this study. This nominal species was described under the generic name 
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FE96FEF059CEF835FDE166AB" box="[464,594,1976,2002]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FE96FEF059CEF835FDFD66AB" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1859" box="[464,590,1976,2002]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Platychyra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Platychyra</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
which is an “unjustified emendation of 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FE96FEF05C12F835FA9D66AA" authority="Rondani, 1856" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1856" box="[1036,1326,1976,2003]" genus="Platychira" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FE96FEF05C12F835FB3166AB" box="[1036,1154,1976,2002]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">Platychira</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FE96FEF05C97F835FA9D66AA" author="Rondani, C." box="[1161,1326,1976,2003]" pageId="347" pageNumber="348" refId="ref368338" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 226 pp. + [2] pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1856">Rondani, 1856</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
” (
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FE96FEF05D59F835FEC9668F" author="O'Hara, J. E. &amp; Cerretti, P. &amp; Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L." pageId="347" pageNumber="348" pagination="1 - 268" refId="ref361577" refString="O'Hara, J. E., Cerretti, P., Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L. (2011) Nomenclatural studies toward a world list of Diptera genus-group names. Part II: Camillo Rondani. Zootaxa, 3141, 1 - 268. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3141.1.1" type="journal article" year="2011">
O’Hara 
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FE96FEF058D9F850FF4C668F" box="[199,255,2012,2038]" italics="true" pageId="347" pageNumber="348">et al.</emphasis>
2011: 147
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
